{"tid":260202,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"WiiU在日本的最後1款遊戲將於5月31日配信","createTime":"2017-05-27T13:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T15:43:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6644468e1237b9db3e13138d598d639d8a379b0a","tid":260202,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:59:29.000Z","msg":"2017/05/27 18:16<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由Rainy Night Creations開發的《死亡屋 再生》（デッドハウス 再生）將於5月31日配信，遊戲為PS4/WiiU雙平台，這也是WiiU日本地區目前最後1款預定發行的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n此遊戲是一款生存恐怖遊戲，主人公為了救被病毒感染的同伴，必須在大屋中尋找抗病毒的疫苗，同時在大屋內有各種謎題陷阱，怪物喪屍徘徊，玩家需要在限制時間內解謎並與喪屍戰鬥，並找到疫苗。房屋的構造每隔30分鐘就會改變一次，需要玩家有合理的判斷和戰略來解決危機。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲PV：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o-Oy1JRZVBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do-Oy1JRZVBY&d=s2Vvds0Rqn8dD5jIACK6EkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a8b83e36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o-Oy1JRZVBY</a>"},{"pid":"cad9a3e2f30347a30f477f9bf3cb0b49bf0755cb","tid":260202,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b4e5b1d3c14024e0f4125f3b8284b8d06bd891","tid":260202,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"任豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45774907d46d371ced3f0283a3244748063c6ef9","tid":260202,"uid":36116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"個style 好 bio hazard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dffa84b9d74080f2033f3642a09949e593e33d","tid":260202,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}